    "creation_date" : 1276116182,
    "answer_id" : 3009781,
    "question_id" : 3009745,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In English:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>It's a <code>List</code> of some type that extends the class <code>HasWord</code>, including <code>HasWord</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>In general the <code>?</code> in generics means any class.  And the <code>extends SomeClass</code> specifies that that object must extend <code>SomeClass</code> (or be that class).</p>\n"
  }, {
