      "comment_id" : 8405790,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "You don&#39;t need wildcards for this, actually: <code>List&lt;HasWord&gt;</code> does just as well for this. The point here is that this variable can contain a <code>List&lt;A&gt;</code> or <code>List&lt;B&gt;</code> as well as a <code>List&lt;HasWord&gt;</code>."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 137377,
